<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>경찰청 통합 진급 사이트</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            height: 100vh;
            background-color: white;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            font-family: 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif;
        }
        .container {
            text-align: center;
        }
        h1 {
            color: #333;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }
        .exam-button {
            padding: 20px 40px;
            font-size: 24px;
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: white;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: background-color 0.3s;
            text-decoration: none;
            display: inline-block;
        }
        .exam-button:hover {
            background-color: #0056b3;
        }
    </style>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+KR:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>경찰청 통합 진급 시험</h1>
        <a href="/exam" class="exam-button">응시하기</a>
    </div>
</body>
</html> 